8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Tidio and Ultimate.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Live Chat, Ai Chatbot, Analytics, Multichannel. Where Tidio pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Ticket Management, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. On the other hand, Ultimate.ai uniquely offers Knowledge Base, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Tidio holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Ultimate.ai scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
9:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Tidio and Ultimate.ai offer flexible pricing models. Tidio has a notable advantage here with its free plan, allowing you to get started without any financial commitment. Ultimate.ai does not currently offer a free tier, which means you will need to pay from day one."}]]}]
